** ISSUE #510
------------------------------------------------------------
10th of May 2026

Hi folks! Only ten days till the KotlinConf. We hope to see many of you in=
 Munich. Feel free to ping us if you want stickers or just to grab a cup o=
f coffee. Enjoy our selection of links for the week=2C

News
